Jake Eastwood (born 3 October 1996) is an English footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Sheffield United.
Having come through the Sheffield United academy he has previously spent time on loan with Sheffield, Gainsborough Trinity, Mickleover Sports, Chesterfield, Scunthorpe United, Kilmarnock, Grimsby Town and Portsmouth.
